column2: "Envelopment of the Dragoncrystals and Ashen particles, complete!"
"...Alright. We've finished setting the stage. The rest is up to you, Sukuna-hime."
"Leave it to me!"
"Here!"
"Gh!"
"...Was that ash?!"
"Kaka, thy expression has finally changed, o' great Goddess of Demise."
"...Sukuna-hime!"
"You... Miko of Harkotan. How could one who is bound to their planet be here?!"
"Truly, now... I am well aware of thy craftiness, but never did I foresee thou wouldst mimic mine ash."
"The Ashen ring which Alma and Xiao have created has at last encircled this region of the cosmos. Teleportation is now but a trifle."
"So focused was thy attention on the assault from ARKS that you paid not a single mind to't."
"...Heheh, hahah! Your entertainment never ceases!"
"However, no manner of trickery can narrow the overwhelming gap in our powers. You have merely expended more energy."
"Someone of your strength could never hope to seal mine away!"
"That, too, is obvious! For what other reason could I have chosen to appear before thee in person?!"
"This is... Ashen wind, and Dragoncrystals...!"

"<%me>, Matoi.
This is my final plan."

"The entire power of ARKS...
I leave it all to you!"
"This...! This power is...! What an odious sight...!"
"Why can you not see that this is the same mistake the Photoners once made?!"
"It's not a mistake."
"It's not a mistake."
"This is to stop you."
"This is to stop you."
"...Then see if you can. You will learn the end result of such folly!"
